3297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f84d880539faaed9d3b887c1d2413ee6514ca380","tid":1693500,"uid":106954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"消防 比啲骨氣出黎啦"},{"pid":"b4279f6620b9b07c7086d5a7226dd35944978b91","tid":1693500,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:07:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16d1b20aa574aa47d7f120ebc3ffbe0079473f6c","tid":1693500,"uid":284695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9a145e09fef59a0239f5bb969bd73213cc0714","tid":1693500,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:10:51.000Z","msg":"要做下功課，填定份表先。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/licensing/general/tc/gls_ppm-fm_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Flicensing%2Fgeneral%2Ftc%2Fgls_ppm-fm_tc.pdf&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=f8972853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/licensing/general/tc/gls_ppm-fm_tc.pdf</a><br />\n行邊區好，各位巴打絲打畀的意見！"},{"pid":"0b58da3d2520fd5e90be776354bc057034bb8016","tid":1693500,"uid":284695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef7ea80bef6b19a9df6913eee9f60777196696db","tid":1693500,"uid":133113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"非常鄉下仔，唔查都唔知。<br />\n原來消防署總部大樓無尖沙咀康莊道1號。<br />\n咁行尖沙咀大家有無意見？"},{"pid":"a338c938a0d0c6a98c193c1def9522c51db8b9be","tid":1693500,"uid":284695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0119aa0bedee3952a358cb7561cb731d2c3c96c2","tid":1693500,"uid":64644,"li